 a sleepy village in the Shire, a young hobbit is entrusted with an...","publication_datetime":"2021-09-16T07:00:00Z","publication_name":"The Lord of the Rings","publisher_summary":"<p><b>This brand-new unabridged audiobook of </b><b><i>The Fellowship of the Ring</i></b><b>, the first part of J. R. R. Tolkien’s epic adventure </b><b><i>The Lord of the Rings</i></b><b>, is read by the BAFTA Award-winning actor, director, and author Andy Serkis.&nbsp;</b></p> <p>In a sleepy village in the Shire, a young hobbit is entrusted with an immense task. He must make a perilous journey across Middle-earth to the Cracks of Doom, there to destroy the Ruling Ring of Power - the only thing that prevents the Dark Lord Sauron’s evil dominion. Thus begins J. R. R. Tolkien’s classic tale of adventure, which continues in <i>The Two Towers</i> and <i>The Return of the King</i>.</p>","rating":{"num_reviews":2958,"overall_distribution":{"average_rating":4.923901477832512,"display_average_rating":"4.9","display_stars":5.0,"num_five_star_ratings":23922,"num_four_star_ratings":1124,"num_one_star_ratings":41,"num_ratings":25375,"num_three_star_ratings":221,"num_two_star_ratings":67},"performance_distribution":{"average_rating":4.947640966628309,"display_average_rating":"4.9","display_stars":5.0,"num_five_star_ratings":21797,"num_four_star_ratings":579,"num_one_star_ratings":62,"num_ratings":22594,"num_three_star_ratings":112,"num_two_star_ratings":44},"story_distribution":{"average_rating":4.921694764862467,"display_average_rating":"4.9","display_stars":5.0,"num_five_star_ratings":21168,"num_four_star_ratings":1084,"num_one_star_ratings":31,"num_ratings":22540,"num_three_star_ratings":214,"num_two_star_ratings":43}},"release_date":"2021-09-16","runtime_length_min":1358,"sku":"BK_RECO_016048","sku_lite":"BK_RECO_016048","subtitle":"Lord of the Rings, Book 1","title":"The Fellowship of the Ring"},{"asin":"B07646TNMP","asset_details":[],"available_codecs":[{"enhanced_codec":"LC_32_22050_stereo","format":"Enhanced","is_kindle_enhanced":true,"name":"aax_22_32"},{"enhanced_codec":"LC_64_22050_stereo","format":"Enhanced","is_kindle_enhanced":true,"name":"aax_22_64"},{"enhanced_codec":"format4","format":"Format4","is_kindle_enhanced":false,"name":"format4"},{"enhanced_codec":"mp42264","format":"Enhanced","is_kindle_enhanced":true,"name":"mp4_22_64"},{"enhanced_codec":"mp42232","format":"Enhanced","is_kindle_enhanced":true,"name":"mp4_22_32"},{"enhanced_codec":"aax","format":"Enhanced","is_kindle_enhanced":false,"name":"aax"}],"category_ladders":[{"ladder":[{"id":"18573518011","name":"History"}],"root":"Genres"},{"ladder":[{"id":"18574641011","name":"Politics & Social Sciences"},{"id":"18574642011","name":"Anthropology"}],"root":"Genres"},{"ladder":[{"id":"18574641011","name":"Politics & Social Sciences"},{"id":"18574731011","name":"Social Sciences"},{"id":"18574733011","name":"Criminology"}],"root":"Genres"},{"ladder":[{"id":"18574641011","name":"Politics & Social Sciences"},{"id":"18574731011","name":"Social Sciences"}],"root":"Genres"}],"content_delivery_type":"SinglePartBook","content_type":"Product","editorial_reviews":["<b>Praise for the Lore podcast</b><br /> <br /> “Truth can often be much scarier than fiction—something [Aaron] Mahnke proves as he dives deep into the world of folklore and the darker side of history in a quest to root out the fragment of truth at the bottom of our fears.”<b><i>—Entertainment Weekly</i></b><br /> <br /> “Unlike so much horror that needs over-the-top viscera to scare you, this podcast leans on history—folklore, myth, the stuff people once thought was true—to tell its tales.”<b><i>—The Atlantic</i></b><br /> <br /> “Narrated by Mahnke in a style that evokes spooky campfire stories, Lore is a history lesson like no other.”<b>—<i>Esquire</i></b>"],"format_type":"unabridged","has_children":false,"is_adult_product":false,"is_listenable":true,"is_preview_enabled":false,"is_purchasability_suppressed":false,"is_vvab":false,"issue_date":"2018-05-29","language":"english","merchandising_summary":"A chilling, lavishly illustrated who’s who of the most despicable people ever to walk the earth, featuring stories from the Lore podcast—now a streaming television series—including “Black Stockings,” “Half-Hanged,” and “The Castle,” as well as rare material. Some monsters are...","publication_datetime":"2018-05-29T07:00:00Z","publication_name":"The World of Lore","publisher_summary":"<b>A chilling, lavishly illustrated who’s who of the most despicable people ever to walk the earth, featuring stories from the Lore podcast—now a streaming television series—including “Black Stockings,” “Half-Hanged,” and “The Castle,” as well as rare material.</b><br /><br /> Some monsters are figments of our imagination. Others are as real as flesh and blood: humans who may look like us, who may walk among us, often unnoticed, occasionally even admired—but whose evil deeds and secret lives, once revealed, mark them as something utterly wicked.<br /> &nbsp;<br /> In this illustrated volume from the host of the hit podcast Lore, you’ll find tales of infamous characters whose veins ran with ice water and whose crimes remind us that truth can be more terrifying than fiction. Aaron Mahnke introduces us to William Brodie, a renowned Scottish cabinetmaker who used his professional expertise to prey on the citizens of Edinburgh and whose rampant criminality behind a veneer of social respectability inspired Robert Louis Stevenson’s classic novella <i>Strange Case of</i> <i>Dr. Jekyll and Mr. Hyde</i>. Then there’s H. H. Holmes, a relentless and elusive con artist who became best known as the terror of Chicago’s 1893 World’s Fair when unwitting guests were welcomed into his “hotel” of horrors . . . never to be seen again. And no rogues’ gallery could leave out Bela Kiss, the Hungarian tinsmith with a taste for the occult and a collection of gasoline drums with women’s bodies inside.<br /> &nbsp;<br /> Brimming with accounts of history’s most heinous real-life fiends, this riveting best-of-the-worst roundup will haunt your thoughts, chill your bones, and leave you wondering if there are mortal monsters lurking even closer than you think.<br /><br /><b>The World of Lore series includes:</b><br /><b>MONSTROUS CREATURES • WICKED MORTALS • DREADFUL PLACES</b>","rating":{"num_reviews":47,"overall_distribution":{"average_rating":4.633375474083438,"display_average_rating":"4.6","display_stars":4.5,"num_five_star_ratings":584,"num_four_star_ratings":143,"num_one_star_ratings":5,"num_ratings":791,"num_three_star_ratings":50,"num_two_star_ratings":9},"performance_distribution":{"average_rating":4.684873949579832,"display_average_rating":"4.7","display_stars":4.5,"num_five_star_ratings":565,"num_four_star_ratings":93,"num_one_star_ratings":4,"num_ratings":714,"num_three_star_ratings":40,"num_two_star_ratings":12},"story_distribution":{"average_rating":4.634696755994359,"display_average_rating":"4.6","display_stars":4.5,"num_five_star_ratings":527,"num_four_star_ratings":118,"num_one_star_ratings":1,"num_ratings":709,"num_three_star_ratings":52,"num_two_star_ratings":11}},"release_date":"2018-05-29","runtime_length_min":610,"sku":"BK_RAND_005362","sku_lite":"BK_RAND_005362","title":"The World of Lore: Wicked Mortals"},{"asin":"B01496V4NM","asset_details":[],"available_codecs":[{"enhanced_codec":"LC_128_44100_stereo","format":"Enhanced","is_kindle_enhanced":true,"name":"aax_44_128"},{"enhanced_codec":"LC_64_44100_stereo","format":"Enhanced","is_kindle_enhanced":true,"name":"aax_44_64"},{"enhanced_codec":"LC_32_22050_stereo","format":"Enhanced","is_kindle_enhanced":true,"name":"aax_22_32"},{"enhanced_codec":"LC_64_22050_stereo","format":"Enhanced","is_kindle_enhanced":true,"name":"aax_22_64"},{"enhanced_codec":"aax","format":"Enhanced","is_kindle_enhanced":false,"name":"aax"}],"category_ladders":[{"ladder":[{"id":"18580518011","name":"Romance"},{"id":"18580522011","name":"Contemporary"}],"root":"Genres"}],"content_delivery_type":"SinglePartBook","content_rating":{"steaminess":"4"},"content_type":"Product","format_type":"unabridged","has_children":false,"is_adult_product":false,"is_listenable":true,"is_preview_enabled":false,"is_purchasability_suppressed":false,"is_vvab":false,"issue_date":"2015-11-03","language":"english","merchandising_summary":"College junior John Logan can get any girl he wants. For this hockey star, life is a parade of parties and hook-ups, but behind his killer grins and easygoing charm, he hides despair....","publication_datetime":"2015-11-03T08:00:00Z","publication_name":"Off-Campus","publisher_summary":"<p>He's a player in more ways than one.... </p> <p>College junior John Logan can get any girl he wants. For this hockey star, life is a parade of parties and hookups, but behind his killer grins and easygoing charm, he hides growing despair about the dead-end road he'll be forced to walk after graduation. A sexy encounter with freshman Grace Ivers is just the distraction he needs, but when a thoughtless mistake pushes her away, Logan plans to spend his final year proving to her that he's worth a second chance. Now he's going to need to up his game.... </p> <p>After a less than stellar freshman year, Grace is back at Briar University, older, wiser, and so over the arrogant hockey player she nearly handed her V-card to. She's not a charity case, and she's not the quiet butterfly she was when they first hooked up. If Logan expects her to roll over and beg like all his other puck bunnies, he can think again. He wants her back? He'll have to work for it. This time around, she'll be the one in the driver's seat, and she plans on driving him wild. </p>","rating":{"num_reviews":426,"overall_distribution":{"average_rating":4.397617274758004,"display_average_rating":"4.4","display_stars":4.5,"num_five_star_ratings":2332,"num_four_star_ratings":1143,"num_one_star_ratings":39,"num_ratings":4029,"num_three_star_ratings":417,"num_two_star_ratings":98},"performance_distribution":{"average_rating":4.184927697441601,"display_average_rating":"4.2","display_stars":4.0,"num_five_star_ratings":1909,"num_four_star_ratings":892,"num_one_star_ratings":130,"num_ratings":3596,"num_three_star_ratings":476,"num_two_star_ratings":189},"story_distribution":{"average_rating":4.444197049819093,"display_average_rating":"4.4","display_stars":4.5,"num_five_star_ratings":2198,"num_four_star_ratings":932,"num_one_star_ratings":27,"num_ratings":3593,"num_three_star_ratings":351,"num_two_star_ratings":85}},"release_date":"2015-11-03","runtime_length_min":611,"sku":"BK_ADBL_025355","sku_lite":"BK_ADBL_025355","thesaurus_subject_keywords":["la_confidential","literature-and-fiction"],"title":"The Mistake"},{"asin":"1039402410","asset_details":[],"available_codecs":[{"enhanced_codec":"format4","format":"Format4","is_kindle_enhanced":false,"name":"format4"},{"enhanced_codec":"LC_64_22050_stereo","format":"Enhanced","is_kindle_enhanced":true,"name":"aax_22_64"},{"enhanced_codec":"LC_128_44100_stereo","format":"Enhanced","is_kindle_enhanced":true,"name":"aax_44_128"},{"enhanced_codec":"LC_64_44100_stereo","format":"Enhanced","is_kindle_enhanced":true,"name":"aax_44_64"},{"enhanced_codec":"LC_32_22050_stereo","format":"Enhanced","is_kindle_enhanced":true,"name":"aax_22_32"},{"enhanced_codec":"mp42232","format":"Enhanced","is_kindle_enhanced":true,"name":"mp4_22_32"},{"enhanced_codec":"mp42264","format":"Enhanced","is_kindle_enhanced":true,"name":"mp4_22_64"},{"enhanced_codec":"mp444128","format":"Enhanced","is_kindle_enhanced":true,"name":"mp4_44_128"},{"enhanced_codec":"mp44464","format":"Enhanced","is_kindle_enhanced":true,"name":"mp4_44_64"},{"enhanced_codec":"aax","format":"Enhanced","is_kindle_enhanced":false,"name":"aax"}],"category_ladders":[{"ladder":[{"id":"18580606011","name":"Science Fiction & Fantasy"},{"id":"18580607011","name":"Fantasy"},{"id":"18580613011","name":"Dragons & Mythical Creatures"}],"root":"Genres"},{"ladder":[{"id":"18580606011","name":"Science Fiction & Fantasy"},{"id":"18580607011","name":"Fantasy"},{"id":"18580615011","name":"Epic"}],"root":"Genres"},{"ladder":[{"id":"18580606011","name":"Science Fiction & Fantasy"},{"id":"18580607011","name":"Fantasy"},{"id":"18580616011","name":"Fairy Tales"}],"root":"Genres"}],"content_delivery_type":"SinglePartBook","content_type":"Product","format_type":"unabridged","has_children":false,"is_adult_product":false,"is_listenable":true,"is_preview_enabled":false,"is_purchasability_suppressed":false,"is_vvab":false,"issue_date":"2021-08-17","language":"english","merchandising_summary":"A human princess. An elven warrior. A betrothal bound in a curse. Today, Aury learned three things; one, she is a princess; two, she might be a powerful mage; and three, a brutal mountain elf is on his way to the kingdom for their marriage. Aury can't escape her newly revealed royal parents...","publication_datetime":"2021-08-17T07:00:00Z","publication_name":"Kingdoms of Lore","publisher_summary":"<p> <b>A human princess. An elven warrior. A betrothal bound in a curse.</b> </p> <p> Today, Aury learned three things; one, she is a princess; two, she might be a powerful mage; and three, a brutal mountain elf is on his way to the kingdom for their marriage. Aury can't escape her newly revealed royal parents quickly enough. If they think she is going to marry some vicious elven warrior mage, they have another thing coming. They claim she's a mage too, but she has yet to prove it. She heads to the magic military order to get her rune-marked staff and learn everything she can. If she becomes the weapon they need instead of her not-if-she-can-help-it husband, they'll send the mountain elf packing, right? If they don't, she will. </p> <p> Filip is certain of three truths; one, he is bound to wed a stubborn mule of a princess; two, the union will give his people the farmland they desperately need; and three, his nightmare of a bride has wild magic that will probably kill him before their wedding day. But he will die before he gives up on winning her hand. War is coming, and the first battle will be fought in the heart. </p> <p> Loosely inspired by the old tales of <i>Sleeping Beauty</i>, this novel is set in the same world as <i>USA Today</i> best-selling author Alisha Klapheke's Dragons Rising series, but listeners can easily start with this book. </p>","rating":{"num_reviews":67,"overall_distribution":{"average_rating":4.301694915254237,"display_average_rating":"4.3","display_stars":4.5,"num_five_star_ratings":173,"num_four_star_ratings":65,"num_one_star_ratings":5,"num_ratings":295,"num_three_star_ratings":35,"num_two_star_ratings":17},"performance_distribution":{"average_rating":4.480701754385965,"display_average_rating":"4.5","display_stars":4.5,"num_five_star_ratings":195,"num_four_star_ratings":53,"num_one_star_ratings":4,"num_ratings":285,"num_three_star_ratings":20,"num_two_star_ratings":13},"story_distribution":{"average_rating":4.186619718309859,"display_average_rating":"4.2","display_stars":4.0,"num_five_star_ratings":158,"num_four_star_ratings":60,"num_one_star_ratings":9,"num_ratings":284,"num_three_star_ratings":36,"num_two_star_ratings":21}},"release_date":"2021-08-17","runtime_length_min":602,"sku":"BK_PODM_002617","sku_lite":"BK_PODM_002617","subtitle":"Kingdoms of Lore, Book 1","title":"Enchanting the Elven Mage"},{"asin":"B09YKG9TJY","asset_details":[],"available_codecs":[{"enhanced_codec":"LC_64_22050_stereo","format":"Enhanced","is_kindle_enhanced":true,"name":"aax_22_64"},{"enhanced_codec":"LC_32_22050_stereo","format":"Enhanced","is_kindle_enhanced":true,"name":"aax_22_32"},{"enhanced_codec":"LC_128_44100_stereo","format":"Enhanced","is_kindle_enhanced":true,"name":"aax_44_128"},{"enhanced_codec":"LC_64_44100_stereo","format":"Enhanced","is_kindle_enhanced":true,"name":"aax_44_64"},{"enhanced_codec":"format4","format":"Format4","is_kindle_enhanced":false,"name":"format4"},{"enhanced_codec":"mp42232","format":"Enhanced","is_kindle_enhanced":true,"name":"mp4_22_32"},{"enhanced_codec":"mp44464","format":"Enhanced","is_kindle_enhanced":true,"name":"mp4_44_64"},{"enhanced_codec":"mp444128","format":"Enhanced","is_kindle_enhanced":true,"name":"mp4_44_128"},{"enhanced_codec":"mp42264","format":"Enhanced","is_kindle_enhanced":true,"name":"mp4_22_64"},{"enhanced_codec":"aax","format":"Enhanced","is_kindle_enhanced":false,"name":"aax"}],"category_ladders":[{"ladder":[{"id":"18574426011","name":"Literature & Fiction"},{"id":"18574456011","name":"Genre Fiction"},{"id":"18574905011","name":"Christian Fiction"},{"id":"18574911011","name":"Science Fiction & Fantasy"},{"id":"18574913011","name":"Science Fiction"}],"root":"Genres"},{"ladder":[{"id":"18580606011","name":"Science Fiction & Fantasy"},{"id":"18580628011","name":"Science Fiction"},{"id":"18580629011","name":"Adventure"}],"root":"Genres"},{"ladder":[{"id":"18580606011","name":"Science Fiction & Fantasy"},{"id":"18580628011","name":"Science Fiction"},{"id":"18580645011","name":"Space Opera"}],"root":"Genres"}],"content_delivery_type":"SinglePartBook","content_type":"Product","editorial_reviews":[""],"format_type":"unabridged","has_children":false,"is_adult_product":false,"is_listenable":true,"is_preview_enabled":false,"is_purchasability_suppressed":false,"is_vvab":false,"issue_date":"2022-04-22","language":"english","merchandising_summary":"<p>Daeson finds himself a prisoner in a tribal world where the law of survival rules. Gone is the hope of the promised homeworld given by the mighty Immortal, Ell Yon. Daeson must fight to restore a future to the Raylean people, but to succeed, he must overcome the marauders of cruel worlds....</p>","publication_datetime":"2022-04-22T20:18:00Z","publication_name":"The Starlore Legacy","publisher_summary":"<p><b>The Raylean people teeter on the edge of annihilation. Can Daeson lead the quest for their promised homeworld?</b></p> <p>Daeson finds himself a prisoner in a tribal world where the law of survival rules. Gone is the hope of the promised homeworld given by the mighty Immortal, Ell Yon. Daeson must fight to restore a future to the Raylean people, but to succeed, he must overcome the marauders of cruel worlds, the tragedy of quantum peril, and the archenemy of the Sovereign Ell Yon, Lord Dracus. The odds are mounting against him. The relentless loyalty of his friend, Tig, sustains him as he rediscovers the power of the Protector. Can he lead the Rayleans to freedom once more?</p>","rating":{"num_reviews":8,"overall_distribution":{"average_rating":4.858974358974359,"display_average_rating":"4.9","display_stars":5.0,"num_five_star_ratings":71,"num_four_star_ratings":5,"num_one_star_ratings":1,"num_ratings":78,"num_three_star_ratings":1,"num_two_star_ratings":0},"performance_distribution":{"average_rating":4.983870967741935,"display_average_rating":"5.0","display_stars":5.0,"num_five_star_ratings":61,"num_four_star_ratings":1,"num_one_star_ratings":0,"num_ratings":62,"num_three_star_ratings":0,"num_two_star_ratings":0},"story_distribution":{"average_rating":4.967741935483871,"display_average_rating":"5.0","display_stars":5.0,"num_five_star_ratings":60,"num_four_star_ratings":2,"num_one_star_ratings":0,"num_ratings":62,"num_three_star_ratings":0,"num_two_star_ratings":0}},"release_date":"2022-04-22","runtime_length_min":453,"sku":"BK_ACX0_305822","sku_lite":"BK_ACX0_305822","subtitle":"The Starlore Legacy, Book 3","thesaurus_subject_keywords":["literature-and-fiction"],"title":"Lore"},{"asin":"B09PSRGX29","asset_details":[],"category_ladders":[{"ladder":[{"id":"18571910011","name":"Arts & Entertainment"},{"id":"18571913011","name":"Art"}],"root":"Genres"},{"ladder":[{"id":"18574426011","name":"Literature & Fiction"},{"id":"18574500011","name":"Literary History & Criticism"}],"root":"Genres"}],"content_delivery_type":"PodcastParent","content_type":"Podcast","continuity":"episodic","episode_count":1006,"format_type":"original_recording","generic_keyword":"d30fac66-a3a4-42a8-8a26-a77458f49da5","has_children":true,"is_adult_product":false,"is_listenable":false,"is_preview_enabled":false,"is_purchasability_suppressed":true,"is_vvab":false,"issue_date":"2023-07-26","language":"english","merchandising_summary":"With thousands of listeners from around the world, you are sure to be entertained, delighted, and thrilled listening to our growing collection of ...","music_id":"d30fac66-a3a4-42a8-8a26-a77458f49da5","new_episode_added_date":"2026-04-01T16:47:31.00047Z","publication_datetime":"2023-07-26T21:41:27Z","publisher_summary":"With thousands of listeners from around the world, you are sure to be entertained, delighted, and thrilled listening to our growing collection of audiobooks. Listen, Download, Follow, Share, Rate 5 Stars, Send in a Voice Message, and Support This Podcast to encourage us to keep adding more content to our Appbly.com podcasts. For a full list of the Free Audiobooks available please scroll through the episodes in the Free Audiobooks podcast or visit the Media > Podcast > Free Audiobooks icon at Appbly.com. If you have any feedback please send us an email using the Contact icon at Appbly.com.","rating":{"num_reviews":6,"overall_distribution":{"average_rating":4.642857142857143,"display_average_rating":"4.6","display_stars":4.5,"num_five_star_ratings":11,"num_four_star_ratings":1,"num_one_star_ratings":0,"num_ratings":14,"num_three_star_ratings":2,"num_two_star_ratings":0},"performance_distribution":{"average_rating":4.5,"display_average_rating":"4.5","display_stars":4.5,"num_five_star_ratings":10,"num_four_star_ratings":2,"num_one_star_ratings":0,"num_ratings":14,"num_three_star_ratings":1,"num_two_star_ratings":1},"story_distribution":{"average_rating":4.5,"display_average_rating":"4.5","display_stars":4.5,"num_five_star_ratings":11,"num_four_star_ratings":1,"num_one_star_ratings":1,"num_ratings":14,"num_three_star_ratings":1,"num_two_star_ratings":0}},"release_date":"2023-07-26","sku":"PD_8001_352937","sku_lite":"PD_8001_352937","thesaurus_subject_keywords":["podcast_books","podcast_arts","talk","podcast_show"],"title":"Free Audiobooks"},{"asin":"B0CDDF4THK","asset_details":[],"available_codecs":[{"enhanced_codec":"LC_64_44100_stereo","format":"Enhanced","is_kindle_enhanced":true,"name":"aax_44_64"},{"enhanced_codec":"LC_32_22050_stereo","format":"Enhanced","is_kindle_enhanced":true,"name":"aax_22_32"},{"enhanced_codec":"LC_128_44100_stereo","format":"Enhanced","is_kindle_enhanced":true,"name":"aax_44_128"},{"enhanced_codec":"LC_64_22050_stereo","format":"Enhanced","is_kindle_enhanced":true,"name":"aax_22_64"},{"enhanced_codec":"aax","format":"Enhanced","is_kindle_enhanced":false,"name":"aax"}],"category_ladders":[{"ladder":[{"id":"18574426011","name":"Literature & Fiction"},{"id":"18574542011","name":"African American"}],"root":"Genres"},{"ladder":[{"id":"18580518011","name":"Romance"},{"id":"18580523011","name":"Fantasy"}],"root":"Genres"},{"ladder":[{"id":"18580606011","name":"Science Fiction & Fantasy"},{"id":"18580607011","name":"Fantasy"},{"id":"18580616011","name":"Fairy Tales"}],"root":"Genres"}],"content_delivery_type":"SinglePartBook","content_type":"Product","format_type":"unabridged","has_children":false,"is_adult_product":false,"is_listenable":true,"is_preview_enabled":false,"is_purchasability_suppressed":false,"is_vvab":false,"issue_date":"2024-02-27","language":"english","merchandising_summary":"A stunning Romantasy debut about an enchanted library, two handsome Fae, and one human who brings them all together. A library with a deadly enchantment. A Fae lord who wants in. A human woman willing to risk it all for a taste of power. In a land ruled by ruthless Fae, twenty-one-year-old Lore...","publication_datetime":"2024-02-27T08:00:00Z","publication_name":"Lore of the Wilds","publisher_summary":"<p><strong>A stunning Romantasy debut about an enchanted library, two handsome Fae, and one human who brings them all together. </strong></p><p><strong>A library with a deadly enchantment. </strong></p><p><strong>A Fae lord who wants in.</strong></p><p><strong>A human woman willing to risk it all for a taste of power.</strong></p><p>In a land ruled by ruthless Fae, twenty-one-year-old Lore Alemeyu’s village is trapped in a forested prison. Lore knows that any escape attempt is futile—her scars are a testament to her past failures. But when her village is threatened, Lore makes a desperate deal with a Fae lord. She will leave her home to catalog/organize an enchanted library that hasn’t been touched in a thousand years. No Fae may enter the library, but there is a chance a human might be able to breach the cursed doors.</p><p>She convinces him that she will risk her life for wealth, but really she’s after the one thing the Fae covet above all: magic of her own.</p><p>As Lore navigates the hostile world outside, she’s forced to rely on two Fae males to survive. Two very different, very dangerous, very attractive Fae males. When undeniable chemistry ignites, she’s not just in danger of losing her life, but her heart to the very creatures she can never trust.</p>","rating":{"num_reviews":74,"overall_distribution":{"average_rating":4.339222614840989,"display_average_rating":"4.3","display_stars":4.5,"num_five_star_ratings":168,"num_four_star_ratings":65,"num_one_star_ratings":6,"num_ratings":283,"num_three_star_ratings":34,"num_two_star_ratings":10},"performance_distribution":{"average_rating":4.4963503649635035,"display_average_rating":"4.5","display_stars":4.5,"num_five_star_ratings":185,"num_four_star_ratings":55,"num_one_star_ratings":3,"num_ratings":274,"num_three_star_ratings":22,"num_two_star_ratings":9},"story_distribution":{"average_rating":4.255474452554744,"display_average_rating":"4.3","display_stars":4.5,"num_five_star_ratings":150,"num_four_star_ratings":67,"num_one_star_ratings":7,"num_ratings":274,"num_three_star_ratings":41,"num_two_star_ratings":9}},"release_date":"2024-02-27","runtime_length_min":651,"sku":"BK_HARP_016126","sku_lite":"BK_HARP_016126","subtitle":"A Novel","title":"Lore of the Wilds"},{"asin":"B0C3NDYNM2","asset_details":[],"available_codecs":[{"enhanced_codec":"LC_32_22050_stereo","format":"Enhanced","is_kindle_enhanced":true,"name":"aax_22_32"},{"enhanced_codec":"LC_128_44100_stereo","format":"Enhanced","is_kindle_enhanced":true,"name":"aax_44_128"},{"enhanced_codec":"LC_64_44100_stereo","format":"Enhanced","is_kindle_enhanced":true,"name":"aax_44_64"},{"enhanced_codec":"LC_64_22050_stereo","format":"Enhanced","is_kindle_enhanced":true,"name":"aax_22_64"},{"enhanced_codec":"mp444128","format":"Enhanced","is_kindle_enhanced":true,"name":"mp4_44_128"},{"enhanced_codec":"mp42232","format":"Enhanced","is_kindle_enhanced":true,"name":"mp4_22_32"},{"enhanced_codec":"mp42264","format":"Enhanced","is_kindle_enhanced":true,"name":"mp4_22_64"},{"enhanced_codec":"mp44464","format":"Enhanced","is_kindle_enhanced":true,"name":"mp4_44_64"},{"enhanced_codec":"aax","format":"Enhanced","is_kindle_enhanced":false,"name":"aax"}],"category_ladders":[{"ladder":[{"id":"18580606011","name":"Science Fiction & Fantasy"},{"id":"18580607011","name":"Fantasy"},{"id":"18580608011","name":"Action & Adventure"}],"root":"Genres"},{"ladder":[{"id":"18580606011","name":"Science Fiction & Fantasy"},{"id":"18580607011","name":"Fantasy"},{"id":"18580615011","name":"Epic"}],"root":"Genres"}],"content_delivery_type":"MultiPartBook","content_type":"Product","format_type":"unabridged","has_children":true,"is_adult_product":false,"is_listenable":true,"is_preview_enabled":false,"is_purchasability_suppressed":false,"is_vvab":false,"issue_date":"2023-07-25","language":"english","merchandising_summary":"<p>You know the drill, right? Die in an unfortunate accident and then get sent before a sultry looking goddess who sets you up for reincarnation. Todd was all set to return to earth and give his soul another ride through the roller coaster called life when something extremely unfortunate happened....</p>","publication_datetime":"2023-07-25T07:00:00Z","publication_name":"The Elemental Realms","publisher_summary":"<p>You know the drill, right? Die in an unfortunate accident and then get sent before a sultry looking goddess who sets you up for reincarnation. Todd was all set to return to earth and give his soul another ride through the roller coaster called life when something extremely unfortunate happened: the Earth was destroyed by a giant meteor.</p> <p>Already primed for Reincarnation, he was given only one other option, but it involved him rising again in an unknown land where magic wasn’t just in the stories. Want more details? So did he! There wasn’t time to ask much, so he went with it! But like all good Isekai stories, he was given a boon, and he asked for an attractive pixy guide to join him on his journey. Or at least when he asked for a fairy, he assumed that the sexy outfit and attractive part was a given. Turns out what they say about assuming is a 100% correct.</p> <p>Reborn as a “Reincarnate”—a bit on the nose with the naming, but whatever—he stumbles his way through his first moments of a new life. His guide is barely any help at all. The grumpy rotund fairy named Frank would rather sleep and drink himself into a stupor than give any practical advice or guidance. Join our reluctant hero as he is born into a place known only as the Nexus and learns what it means to be a Guardian. How much work must he do before he can just settle down and relax for a minute?</p>","rating":{"num_reviews":9,"overall_distribution":{"average_rating":3.761904761904762,"display_average_rating":"3.8","display_stars":4.0,"num_five_star_ratings":17,"num_four_star_ratings":9,"num_one_star_ratings":3,"num_ratings":42,"num_three_star_ratings":8,"num_two_star_ratings":5},"performance_distribution":{"average_rating":4.6,"display_average_rating":"4.6","display_stars":4.5,"num_five_star_ratings":23,"num_four_star_ratings":10,"num_one_star_ratings":0,"num_ratings":35,"num_three_star_ratings":2,"num_two_star_ratings":0},"story_distribution":{"average_rating":3.8,"display_average_rating":"3.8","display_stars":4.0,"num_five_star_ratings":16,"num_four_star_ratings":6,"num_one_star_ratings":3,"num_ratings":35,"num_three_star_ratings":6,"num_two_star_ratings":4}},"release_date":"2023-07-25","runtime_length_min":1090,"sku":"BK_DRMS_011312","sku_lite":"BK_DRMS_011312","subtitle":"The Elemental Realms, Book 1","title":"Nexus Guardian"},{"asin":"B0F3B475X8","asset_details":[],"available_codecs":[{"enhanced_codec":"LC_64_44100_stereo","format":"Enhanced","is_kindle_enhanced":true,"name":"aax_44_64"},{"enhanced_codec":"LC_128_44100_stereo","format":"Enhanced","is_kindle_enhanced":true,"name":"aax_44_128"},{"enhanced_codec":"LC_32_22050_stereo","format":"Enhanced","is_kindle_enhanced":true,"name":"aax_22_32"},{"enhanced_codec":"LC_64_22050_stereo","format":"Enhanced","is_kindle_enhanced":true,"name":"aax_22_64"},{"enhanced_codec":"aax","format":"Enhanced","is_kindle_enhanced":false,"name":"aax"}],"category_ladders":[{"ladder":[{"id":"18573518011","name":"History"},{"id":"18573526011","name":"Americas"},{"id":"18573540011","name":"United States"},{"id":"18573545011","name":"Indigenous Peoples"}],"root":"Genres"},{"ladder":[{"id":"18574839011","name":"Religion & Spirituality"},{"id":"18575015011","name":"Other Religions, Practices & Sacred Texts"}],"root":"Genres"}],"content_delivery_type":"SinglePartBook","content_type":"Product","format_type":"unabridged","has_children":false,"is_adult_product":false,"is_listenable":true,"is_preview_enabled":false,"is_purchasability_suppressed":false,"is_vvab":true,"issue_date":"2025-04-02","language":"english","merchandising_summary":"Unravel the Meaning Behind Ancient Native American Myths Long before the written word, Indigenous tribes across North America passed down powerful ...","publication_datetime":"2025-04-02T02:16:00Z","publisher_summary":"<b>Unravel the Meaning Behind Ancient Native American Myths</b><p>Long before the written word, Indigenous tribes across North America passed down <b>powerful oral traditions</b>—stories of mighty <b>Thunderbirds</b>, <b>trickster spirits</b>, and <b>dark omens</b> that shaped their understanding of the world. But these myths are <b>more than just stories</b>—they reveal <b>deep spiritual insights, survival wisdom, and the forces that shaped Native cultures.</b></p><p>In <b>Native American Myths: Stories & Their Hidden Meanings</b>, explore <b>not only the myths themselves</b> but also the <b>deeper symbolism, history, and impact they have had on Indigenous traditions and beliefs.</b></p><p>✔ <b>Retellings of 25 fascinating myths</b>, from creation stories to legendary battles<br />✔ <b>The hidden meanings behind each myth</b>—what they teach about nature, balance, and human nature<br />✔ <b>How these stories shaped Indigenous beliefs, rituals, and daily life</b><br />✔ <b>Comparisons with myths from other cultures</b>, revealing universal themes<br />✔ <b>The legacy of Native myths today</b>—how they continue to inspire modern storytelling</p><p>This book is <b>perfect for history lovers, mythology enthusiasts, and anyone fascinated by the wisdom of Indigenous cultures.</b></p><p>📖 <b>More than just myths—this book explores their lasting impact.</b></p>","rating":{"num_reviews":4,"overall_distribution":{"average_rating":3.2222222222222223,"display_average_rating":"3.2","display_stars":3.0,"num_five_star_ratings":3,"num_four_star_ratings":2,"num_one_star_ratings":2,"num_ratings":9,"num_three_star_ratings":0,"num_two_star_ratings":2},"performance_distribution":{"average_rating":3.7777777777777777,"display_average_rating":"3.8","display_stars":4.0,"num_five_star_ratings":4,"num_four_star_ratings":2,"num_one_star_ratings":1,"num_ratings":9,"num_three_star_ratings":1,"num_two_star_ratings":1},"story_distribution":{"average_rating":3.3333333333333335,"display_average_rating":"3.3","display_stars":3.5,"num_five_star_ratings":4,"num_four_star_ratings":1,"num_one_star_ratings":2,"num_ratings":9,"num_three_star_ratings":0,"num_two_star_ratings":2}},"release_date":"2025-04-02","runtime_length_min":188,"sku":"VV_8001_183319","sku_lite":"VV_8001_183319","subtitle":"Ancient Legends and Folklore from Indigenous Tribes","text_to_speech":"TANDEM","thesaurus_subject_keywords":["tandem"],"title":"Native American Myths"},{"asin":"1713580993","asset_details":[],"available_codecs":[{"enhanced_codec":"LC_128_44100_stereo","format":"Enhanced","is_kindle_enhanced":true,"name":"aax_44_128"},{"enhanced_codec":"LC_32_22050_stereo","format":"Enhanced","is_kindle_enhanced":true,"name":"aax_22_32"},{"enhanced_codec":"LC_64_44100_stereo","format":"Enhanced","is_kindle_enhanced":true,"name":"aax_44_64"},{"enhanced_codec":"LC_64_22050_stereo","format":"Enhanced","is_kindle_enhanced":true,"name":"aax_22_64"},{"enhanced_codec":"format4","format":"Format4","is_kindle_enhanced":false,"name":"format4"},{"enhanced_codec":"mp42232","format":"Enhanced","is_kindle_enhanced":true,"name":"mp4_22_32"},{"enhanced_codec":"mp444128","format":"Enhanced","is_kindle_enhanced":true,"name":"mp4_44_128"},{"enhanced_codec":"mp42264","format":"Enhanced","is_kindle_enhanced":true,"name":"mp4_22_64"},{"enhanced_codec":"mp44464","format":"Enhanced","is_kindle_enhanced":true,"name":"mp4_44_64"},{"enhanced_codec":"aax","format":"Enhanced","is_kindle_enhanced":false,"name":"aax"}],"category_ladders":[{"ladder":[{"id":"18574597011","name":"Mystery, Thriller & Suspense"},{"id":"18574606011","name":"Mystery"},{"id":"18574617011","name":"Police Procedurals"}],"root":"Genres"},{"ladder":[{"id":"18574597011","name":"Mystery, Thriller & Suspense"},{"id":"18574606011","name":"Mystery"},{"id":"18574620011","name":"Women Sleuths"}],"root":"Genres"},{"ladder":[{"id":"18574597011","name":"Mystery, Thriller & Suspense"},{"id":"18574621011","name":"Thriller & Suspense"},{"id":"18574639011","name":"Suspense"}],"root":"Genres"}],"content_delivery_type":"SinglePartBook","content_type":"Product","format_type":"unabridged","has_children":false,"is_adult_product":false,"is_listenable":true,"is_preview_enabled":false,"is_purchasability_suppressed":false,"is_vvab":false,"issue_date":"2021-06-01","language":"english","merchandising_summary":"<p>True crime podcaster Trinity Scott is chasing breakout success, and her brand-new serial may get her there. Her subject is Clayton Jay Pelley....</p>","publication_datetime":"2021-06-01T07:00:00Z","publisher_summary":"<p><b>A true crime podcast yields new revelations about a shocking murder in a riveting novel of suspense by </b><b><i>Washington Post</i></b><b> and Amazon Charts bestselling author Loreth Anne White.</b></p> <p>True crime podcaster Trinity Scott is chasing breakout success, and her brand-new serial may get her there. Her subject is Clayton Jay Pelley. More than two decades ago, the respected family man and guidance counselor confessed to the brutal murder of teenage student Leena Rai. But why he killed her has always been a mystery.</p> <p>In a series of exclusive interviews from prison, Clayton discloses to Trinity the truth about what happened that night beneath Devil’s Bridge. It’s not what anyone in the Pacific Northwest town of Twin Falls expects. Clayton says he didn’t do it. Was he lying then? Or now?</p> <p>As her listeners increase and ratings skyrocket, Trinity is missing a key player in the story: Rachel Walczak, the retired detective who exposed Pelley’s twisted urges and put him behind bars. She’s not interested in playing Clayton’s game - until Trinity digs deeper and the podcast’s reverb widens. Then Rachel begins to question everything she thinks she knows about the past.</p> <p>With each of Clayton’s teasing reveals, one thing is clear: he’s not the only one in Twin Falls with a secret.</p>","rating":{"num_reviews":267,"overall_distribution":{"average_rating":4.366262034323985,"display_average_rating":"4.4","display_stars":4.5,"num_five_star_ratings":1366,"num_four_star_ratings":669,"num_one_star_ratings":35,"num_ratings":2389,"num_three_star_ratings":252,"num_two_star_ratings":67},"performance_distribution":{"average_rating":4.217931034482759,"display_average_rating":"4.2","display_stars":4.0,"num_five_star_ratings":1175,"num_four_star_ratings":560,"num_one_star_ratings":77,"num_ratings":2175,"num_three_star_ratings":256,"num_two_star_ratings":107},"story_distribution":{"average_rating":4.425207756232687,"display_average_rating":"4.4","display_stars":4.5,"num_five_star_ratings":1339,"num_four_star_ratings":536,"num_one_star_ratings":36,"num_ratings":2166,"num_three_star_ratings":200,"num_two_star_ratings":55}},"release_date":"2021-06-01","runtime_length_min":702,"sku":"BK_BRLL_013176","sku_lite":"BK_BRLL_013176","subtitle":"A Novel","thesaurus_subject_keywords":["literature-and-fiction"],"title":"Beneath Devil's Bridge"}],"response_groups":["product_desc","always-returned","product_extended_attrs","rating","category_ladders","product_attrs"],"total_results":4889}